<HL>
   Thursday's Markets:
   Stocks Drop
   32.42 Points
   On Tax Talk
   ---
   Trading Is Very Thin;
   Bond Prices Also Sink
   But Dollar Is Mixed
   ----
   By Christopher Winans
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/06/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C1
</SO>
<IN>
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
STOCK INDEXES (NDX)
MONETARY NEWS, FOREIGN EXCHANGE, TRADE (MON)
